theorem not_ring_char_dvd_of_invertible {t : ℕ} [Invertible (t : K)] : ¬ring_char K ∣ t :=
  by
  rw [← ring_char.spec, ← ne.def]
  exact nonzero_of_invertible (t : K)
#align not_ring_char_dvd_of_invertible not_ring_char_dvd_of_invertible
